  • public class SimpleTextColumn
extends AmpDifferentialColumn<TextCell>
    a simple text column which fetches its input from a view which contains 3 or more columns:
    1. amp_activity_id (or pledge_id) 2. payload (text) 3. entity_id (e.g. sector_id, donor_id etc) All the extra columns are ignored
